title: Full House | Snowboarding 2007 Silent Progression Greece
description:
Full House is a two-year trip video featuring some of the best Greek riding, and it was released on December 2007. Through this 30 minute video the crew travels to Parnitha, Parnasso, Mayrhoften, Vasilitsa, Les2Alpes and some other random spots on their way. The sections of the video are divided according to the locations. The movie is filmed with the Sony FX1 camera on normal DV 16:9 widescreen quality.
